prompts.frontCover: A charming and humorous watercolor illustration of a cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, slightly askew party hat, hanging upside down from a tree branch. The sloth is holding a single, unlit birthday candle with a look of immense, slow-motion concentration, as if it's taken all year to get this far. Below the sloth, the words "happy birthday" are elegantly written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The style is a flat 2D watercolor painting with soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the sloth and leaves.
